      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_247gc' title='Col. 247GC &mdash; HL Deb 02 February 2004 vol 656 c247GC' name='column_247gc' href='#column_247gc' rel='bookmark'>247GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-03102'>
