            On sample counts, I am grateful for the Minister's assurances about the definition of same or similar being covered by indictment rules. I will not say that that is a reminder to me, because it is new to me&#x2014;this is not my field of operation. I will need carefully to
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_269gc' title='Col. 269GC &mdash; HL Deb 02 February 2004 vol 656 c269GC' name='column_269gc' href='#column_269gc' rel='bookmark'>269GC</a>
